# Hermes 4.3 36B (Nous Research) — the "smarter" option, official GGUF.
# Q4_K_M ≈ 22 GB. num_ctx is 65536 because Hermes Agent requires a ≥64K window;
# the model natively supports 512K so this is well within range. A 64K KV cache
# is large — pair with the ollama.service KV-cache quantization drop-in
# (OLLAMA_FLASH_ATTENTION=1 + OLLAMA_KV_CACHE_TYPE=q8_0) so it fits the 24 GB GPU
# with less CPU spill. Expect heavier CPU offload than the 8k default regardless.
FROM hf.co/NousResearch/Hermes-4.3-36B-GGUF:Q4_K_M
PARAMETER num_ctx 65536
PARAMETER temperature 0.7
